-| Anti-Pattern | Why | Use Instead |
-|---|---|---|
-| Auto-advancing hero carousels | Engagement drops 90%+ past slide 1 | Static hero with strong headline, or manual tabbed showcase |
-| Hamburger menus on desktop | Hides primary navigation | Full nav bar; reserve hamburger for
